SQL_CODE_SRC: SELECT '[p_DAR_REF]' AS DAR,'[p_objet]' AS idObjet,'[p_RA]' AS RA,'[p_COL]' AS COL,'[p_ROW]' AS ROW,'[p_PERD]' AS PERD,Sum([VALR_INDC]) AS VAL FROM [p_CUBE] WHERE CODE_INDC = [p_INDI] GROUP BY '[p_DAR_REF]','[p_objet]','[p_RA]','[p_COL]' ,'[p_ROW]' ,'[p_PERD]'
